extract intensities and annotations from MQ proteinGroups.txt

Source: R/tidyMS_MQProteinGroups.R
tidyMQ_ProteinGroups.Rd

extract intensities and annotations from MQ proteinGroups.txt

tidyMQ_ProteinGroups(MQProteinGroups)

Arguments

MQProteinGroups

data.frame generated with read.csv("peptide.txt",sep="\t", stringsAsFactors=FALSE)

See also

Other MaxQuant: INTERNAL_FUNCTIONS_BY_FAMILY, MaxQuant, tidyMQ_Evidence(), tidyMQ_Peptides()

Examples

library(prolfqua)
protein_txt <- system.file("samples/maxquant_txt/tiny2.zip",package = "prolfqua")
protein_txt <- read.csv(unz(protein_txt,"proteinGroups.txt"), header=TRUE, stringsAsFactors = FALSE, sep="\t")
mq_proteins <-tidyMQ_ProteinGroups(protein_txt)
